DOC.HEADLINE: BRIEFLY : BANKING & FINANCE
DOC.TEXT: Five-Year Treasury_Notes Yield Rises : Yields on the five-year Treasury_notes rose at auction to the highest level in 15 months.The high yield was 5.91 % , up from 5.61 % at the last auction on Feb . 24 . It was the highest auction rate since five-year note yields hit 6.03 % on Dec . 23 , 1992 . The notes will carry a coupon rate of 5.875 % with each $ 10 # 000 in face_value selling for $ 9 # 985.00. A total of $ 11 billion in notes were sold_out of bids totaling $ 28.1 billion .
